<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- yjrḥ yʿṣb ysḥq ysẖfy ymsḥ dmʿy bḥbh ạlṣạfy
 yrtạḥ qlby wyhrb ḥzny lmạ yạkẖdny fy ḥḍnh ạldạfy
 ạlqrạr- ydy slạm rgẖm ạlạ̉zmạt yʿlạ ạlsẖkr fwq ạlạ̉nạt
 wạlqlb yfyḍ bạltrnymạt rby dạ ạ̹lh ạltʿwyḍạt
 2- ysndny wydạwy ậlạmy blmsạt lṭf wḥnyh
 ynʿsẖny wyḥyy ly ạ̉mạly bhmsạt ʿṭf wtʿzyh
 3- kl ạlạ̉sẖyạʾ tʿml llkẖyr dạ ykẖlynạ mạ ntdẖmrsẖ
 wạ̉mạnth mạfyhạsẖ tgẖyyr rby ḥkym mạ bygẖlṭsẖy
 4- myn gẖyrh yqdr ydạwynạ ạ̉ṣlh mjrb mn qblynạ
 yrḥmnạ wymsk bạ̹ydynạ yrtẖy lḍʿfnạ wyqwynạ
 5-bṣlạḥh rạḥ nsẖhd ʿly̱ ṭwl whạnhtf lh bạ̉ʿly̱ ạlạ̉nạsẖyd
 wẓrwfnạ ạ̉n ywm ʿạkst hạ nqwl dy ạ̉mạnth fy kl ạlmwạʿyd</lyrics>
<title>yjrḥ yʿṣb</title>
